%# Matières grasses

^un sujet // {"headword":"sujet","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^fondamental // {"headword":"fondamental","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?À ce sujet, quel principe fondamental est souvent méconnu ?
Il est **plus important de bien les choisir** que d'en limiter l'apport.

^un lipide // {"headword":"lipide","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?Quels lipides doivent être privilégiés ?
Les lipides **insaturés**.

^une graisse // {"headword":"graisse","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^insaturé // {"headword":"insaturé","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^un avantage // {"headword":"avantage","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
~?Quel est l'avantage des graisses insaturées ?
^un risque // {"headword":"risque","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^une maladie // {"headword":"maladie","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^diminuer // {"headword":"diminuer","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Elles **diminuent les risques de maladies**.

~?Où trouve-t-on des graisses insaturées ?
^une huile végétale // {"headword":"huile végétale","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^une noix // {"headword":"noix","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^une graine // {"headword":"graine","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^un poisson // {"headword":"poisson","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
Dans les **huiles végétales**, les **noix**, les **graines**, et le **poisson**.

^néfaste // {"headword":"néfaste","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?Quels lipides sont le plus néfastes ?
Les lipides **transformés**.

^une santé // {"headword":"santé","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^impact // {"headword":"impact","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^négatif // {"headword":"négatif","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?Quels lipides ont un impact plutôt négatif sur la santé ?
Les lipides **saturés**.

~?Où trouve-t-on des graisses saturées ?
^une viande rouge // {"headword":"viande rouge","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^un beurre // {"headword":"beurre","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^un fromage // {"headword":"fromage","category":"noun","gender":"masculine","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^une huile de palme // {"headword":"huile de palme","category":"noun","gender":"feminine","cefrLevel":"B1"}
Dans la **viande rouge**, le **beurre**, le **fromage**, et l'**huile de palme**.

%# Fats

^the subject // {"headword":"subject","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^fundamental // {"headword":"fundamental","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"C1"}
~?On this subject, what fundamental principle is often overlooked?
It is **more important to choose them well** than to limit their intake.

^the lipid // {"headword":"lipid","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
~?Which lipids should be favoured?
**Unsaturated** lipids.

^the fat // {"headword":"fat","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^unsaturated // {"headword":"unsaturated","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^the advantage // {"headword":"advantage","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?What is the advantage of unsaturated fats?
^the risk // {"headword":"risk","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the disease // {"headword":"disease","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^reduce // {"headword":"reduce","category":"verb","cefrLevel":"B1"}
They **reduce the risk of diseases**.

~?Where are unsaturated fats found?
^the vegetable oil // {"headword":"vegetable oil","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the nut // {"headword":"nut","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the seed // {"headword":"seed","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A2"}
^the fish // {"headword":"fish","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
In **vegetable oils**, **nuts**, **seeds**, and **fish**.

^harmful // {"headword":"harmful","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?Which lipids are the most harmful?
**Transformed** lipids.

^the health // {"headword":"health","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^impact // {"headword":"impact","category":"other","cefrLevel":"B2"}
^negative // {"headword":"negative","category":"adjective","cefrLevel":"B1"}
~?Which lipids have a rather negative impact on health?
**Saturated** lipids.

~?Where are saturated fats found?
^the red meat // {"headword":"red meat","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B1"}
^the butter // {"headword":"butter","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the cheese // {"headword":"cheese","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"A1"}
^the palm oil // {"headword":"palm oil","category":"noun","cefrLevel":"B2"}
In **red meat**, **butter**, **cheese**, and **palm oil**.
